import { InputGroup, Container, Row, FormControl } from 'react-bootstrap'

const Home = () => {
    return (
        <Container>
            <Row>
                <InputGroup size="lg">
                    <InputGroup.Prepend>
                        <InputGroup.Text id="inputGroup-sizing-lg">Large</InputGroup.Text>
                    </InputGroup.Prepend>
                    <FormControl aria-label="Large" aria-describedby="inputGroup-sizing-sm" />
                </InputGroup>

            </Row>
        </Container>
    )
}

export default Home
